{"type": "article", "id": 42838, "title": "UA 签下 A$AP Rocky，以及，Vans 出了“旗袍”款一脚蹬 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-10T03:18:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1733, "name": "Viktor & Rolf"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 22806, "name": "Herschel"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 24721, "name": "UA"}, {"id": 32154, "name": "西尔斯"}, {"id": 29001, "name": "A$AP Rocky"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170710093037OF0gbh2l4yLdBITN.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/under-armour-aap-rocky-said-to-be-collaborating-on-sneakers-10942176/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>UA 将签下饶舌歌手 A$AP Rocky</strong></a> | 日前，Under Armour 传出要与饶舌歌手 A$AP Rocky 合作的消息，这位人气歌手的加盟将帮助 UA 在球鞋系列上获得增长。 A$AP Rocky 不仅曾先后与 adidas Originals、J.W.Anderson 和 Guess 展开联名，还经常亮相各大时装周头排。A$AP Rocky 被 UA 寄予重塑品牌的希望。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/sears-added-8-sears-stores-35-kmart-sites-closure-list-edward-s-lampert-10941717/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>西尔斯百货持续转型</strong></a> | 美国老牌百货公司西尔斯持续转型，宣布将关闭 8 家门店和 35 家 Kmart，自从 2012 年以来，西尔斯已经关闭了将近一半数量的百货商场和 Kmart。该集团的董事长兼首席执行官 Edward S.Lampert 称，西尔斯将继续关闭无利可图的门店，往电商上投入更多。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/opening-ceremony-vans-vault-slip-on-qi-pao-part-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国 Opening Ceremony 与 Vans 合作推出了一款“旗袍”主题系列一脚蹬</a>。该系列共有红、蓝、黑、金四色，刺绣图案遍布鞋面，现已登陆 Opening Ceremony。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105100nqlmuF3XtQ1Uo2EJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105100xeba1oX3iUv2kumq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105100Ndk5r2VPFo6EJ8XD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105101e6IOPwpzZoTG0y3Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/herschel-supply-first-apparel-collection-voyage\" rel=\"nofollow\">以包袋起家的加拿大品牌 Herschel Supply 日前发布了首个服装系列。 </a></p><p>该系列以 Voyage 为名，采用了轻薄面料打造，当中的所有单品都可以轻松折叠收纳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105034o5bHgK8F7CxsaGqr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105033lnQdDV2kWTzKGSJZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105033erQKbiOmwFyX6Lk7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105033KYhA1HIaXMc6JzBw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105033y6p93fubRLmqgUGi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105032tl25nNDAiobKsuI1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105033Mtp9fOySFLJGQ648.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105032bfvhJ5nqc38CZT9k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105032v6A9OnmJByVWbHxU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105038o5De4MZPYad2nWGg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/adidas-boost-slides\" rel=\"nofollow\">搭载 BOOST 缓震技术的阿迪达斯拖鞋全面曝光。</a>在网上流传的 BOOST 技术的样鞋中，除了白蓝配色外，还有全黑的 NEIGHBORHOOD 联名版本。目前，关于这双拖鞋的具体发售信息还未公布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105515BSIOexLqGtRFTXHr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105514cFfGPlk3AX8vpCgn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105512rwiAySBz7C2pQPNK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105513mfbSqxHNnYvAa2wg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105514y3SMsHBzcJGjbrVv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105512HVYiKMsOBayctupS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707101055143IrJcqKVMOXtEaUg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105512IlOC2UuwWHKfEZjz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>庆祝位于伦敦 Albemarle Street 的英国首家门店开幕，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/thom-browne-2017-summer-tennis-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thom Browne 特地举办了一场网球赛，还推出了一个特别限量系列</a>。包括尼龙运动套装、牛津衬衫、棉麻西装外套、麂皮雕花皮鞋、皮革背包以及毛圈布发带和护腕等丰富单品，目前该系列已在 Thom Browne 伦敦门店发售，将于 7 月 11 日登录全球其它门店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105007lXu2zakB58PCRfpc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105007sKkO7njJaHo2eGmE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105008ZMhNKT76CekyUiVc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105009cwBtX0br4PNG98uY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707101050098xsIAf6Y3JBTVOC4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105010jNLTbaUtzhJXdADl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105011gEWF6R0Ytj9pXwzM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105011wT2DqnlKaRdAgQ6P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500457\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707101050118CWiha0mk6BusAcM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105012CO7nBAIfqHoYSvda.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105012pKCEmfZQnc7ObJ0M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500457\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710105013aRue731SG6OIQhjU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/nikelab-07-kmtr-bordeaux\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 机能鞋款 NikeLab 07 KMTR 发布了两款新配色，酒红和金黄色</a>。没有了 ACG 字样的 07 KMTR 鞋身更为干净，这两双鞋已登录 Hanon，定价为 120 英镑。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104950RFMyabkZsQ8YSJ2G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104950UmNrgsucFlqwzy0I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104950GBeCgwFtnzXDUoQ3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667269\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104950VFZsj0B7GCLJ8frb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666320\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104950N6UAMnGm4jxX5ybl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707101049504jOncyqmz6EVM829.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上周于高丽高定秀上发布的<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/parsons-student-accuse-viktor-rolf-of-copying-concepts\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Viktor &amp; Rolf</a>，凭借着大头娃娃模特引起了极大的关注。但在发布会落幕后不久，该品牌的这个创意就被指出涉嫌抄袭。 </p><p>据称，来自 Parsons School of Design 设计学院的学生 Terrence Zhou 在两个月前向 Viktor &amp; Rolf 投递了实习申请，并附上了 Plastic Surgery 作品集，后因不持有欧盟护照而被拒绝。Terrence 发现，Viktor &amp; Rolf 秀场上的作品与自己的设计有惊人的相似之处，遂发布 Instagram 指出。但 Viktor &amp; Rolf 目前还未作出回应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707101049404lYCrJI2EZSVjv5R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.748750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170710104940oCN4rdiFcahkW9M7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.992500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/herschel-supply-first-apparel-collection-voyage\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}